                <note rend="inline" type="source">890F.515/21: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Minister Resident in Saudi Arabia</hi> (<persName
                        type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Moose</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Jidda</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1943-07-26T13:00:00+03:06"
                            >July 26, 1943—1 p.m.</date>
                        <lb/> [Received 6:08 p.m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>73. My 66, July 14, 6 p.m. Saudi Government agreed on July 21 to accept from oil
                    company rupee equivalent of $500,000.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Moose</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
